explination of seeders and leechers:

Seeders- These people have 100% of the file your trying to download. you want them to stay connected to you

Leechers- These are other people downloading the same file as you. you dont want these people for 2 reasons:

1. if they have a smaller percentage than you their computer may download from what you have

2. they take up the seeders bandwith
